schools.name: Fontana A. B. Miller High School

data.description: Welcome home to this 3-bedroom residence, ideally situated in a prime location close to schools, freeways, and shopping centers. This charming home offers comfort, convenience, and functionality, making it an excellent choice for families. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The generous living room has lots of natural light, providing a cozy and inviting space to relax.The well-appointed kitchen is a chef's delight Whether you're hosting a formal dinner party or enjoying a casual family gathering. The home boasts three spacious bedrooms,  The primary bedroom features a bathroom, providing privacy and convenience. The additional bathrooms easily accessible for family members or guests. The low-maintenance landscaping ensures effortless upkeep. Lets make this your NEW HOME!
